  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 268bf36e2c95048f4b4ca0fcdf827688, type: 3}
  m_Name: Envelope1
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueData
  SpeakerName: Dialogue
  lines:
  - "Hey there lately I\u2019ve been feeling a cool draft by the window in the kitchen."
  - In the night time it gets really cold and it prevents me from having my late
    night snack. Every time I go in there I have to wear something to keep me warm.
  - 'I would appreciate it if you can find out why there is a draft in there. '
